{"title":"Imipenem-Cilastatina-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Urología/Imipenem-Cilastatina-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Imipenem-Cilastatina","guid":"jqdWLrQdeoZuUy-nUUPO-w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1. Generalidades:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Clase: Carbapenem.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Espectro: Amplio (Gram-positivos, Gram-negativos, anaerobios).","guid":"_PmTb6muO-6KjvFpc8mvVQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• No cubre: MRSA, E. faecium, Enterococos resistentes a vancomicina, Stenotrophomonas sp.","guid":"5lCSEIzELs9FdvqjC8ElCw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Estabilidad: Inestable en solución → No para infusión prolongada ambulatoria.","guid":"_fxNNBp4jMXpCv_Ni22OIw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Riesgo: Mayor riesgo de convulsiones vs. otros carbapenems.","guid":"CiYLRbRtMbRZ5NoBqRvAjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"2. Mecanismo de Acción:","guid":"ei0mt9Mx69hlge9YEreJcg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Cilastatina: Inhibe la degradación de Imipenem por dehidropeptidasa renal.","guid":"daCl6m9VOVA9qTznIHJElg","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"3. Dosis y Ajustes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Dosis\\NAdultos:","guid":"h-l6_VfioCgFYIeWsR7bng","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Usual: 500 mg IV c/6h o 1 g IV c/8h.","guid":"Q1YCURplsFQ8Jyh6bbclFQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Para P. aeruginosa: 3-4 g/día, dividido c/8h o c/6h.","guid":"XwJu0NGNRu3JoVzAfoUXPw","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"• Dosis\\NPediátrica:","guid":"OgGk7zpI0vh1thH9wJgfiA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• <1 semana: 25 mg/kg c/12h.","guid":"bNnsSYygVzxYEM-x_09FXA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• 1-4 semanas: 25 mg/kg c/8h.","guid":"36q_1wamCq-gd-54gjvpvw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• 4 semanas-3 meses: 25 mg/kg c/6h.","guid":"NL4XMv5RSwR39P7amthMzg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• ≥3 meses: 15-25 mg/kg c/6h.","guid":"iEmjjMb-Y1X05F-wdiQvCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"9","text":"• Ajuste Renal:\\NSegún CrCl:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl ≥90: Sin ajuste.","guid":"sTAOhsh29lcsLlk3htHz1Q","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl 60-90: 400-500 mg c/6-8h.","guid":"Q9tpDLcpsXz-GMuplbq86Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl 30-60: 300-500 mg c/6-8h.","guid":"P6cDJCbovOZzUj_-lZuUwQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl 15-30: 200-500 mg c/6-12h.","guid":"P_SSJkmfp5IKSN_-EZYbTA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"• Diálisis: Ajustar dosis post-diálisis.","guid":"sVfL3qqCIoVJERCe39IP0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"9","text":"• Ajuste Hepático: Ninguno.","guid":"pI2H93pQ3SV14h0r2BI-Dw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"9","text":"• Otros Ajustes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Obesidad: Ninguno.","guid":"61-7qDp62ntYLMQmpdEZ-g","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• ECMO: 750-1000 mg c/6h (según PK, no datos clínicos).","guid":"lnrAr0luogbQ7en5tl2LjQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"4. Efectos\\NAdversos:","guid":"WaHsJXAnjDa1a8K5k4epfw","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• Convulsiones.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Flebitis local (3%), fiebre (3%), rash, anafilaxia, enfermedad del suero, Coombs positivo (2%), neutropenia, eosinofilia, trombocitopenia, PT/PTT\\Nprolongado (raro), náuseas/vómitos (2%), diarrea (2%), colitis por C. difficile, aumento de BUN/Creatinina, cefalea, confusión, ototoxicidad.","guid":"7mJFfo1z2-LRvft1hu8SZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"• Cilastatina: Previene toxicidad renal y la hidrólisis de imipenem.","guid":"FKtaX9W-HSsHBboDUXtYxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"5. Riesgo en Embarazo\\Ny Lactancia:","guid":"stNzWbas1XzJBRBb23Cl0g","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Categoría FDA: C.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Lactancia: Seguro, monitorizar efectos GI en el lactante.","guid":"jFVf3ywkPQAlI0iKxNF1Gg","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"6. Consideraciones\\Nde Stewardship:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Punto de corte de susceptibilidad (1 µg/mL): Disminuye la susceptibilidad\\Npara ciertas Enterobacteriaceae en comparación con otros carbapenems.","guid":"oLtxEuSXaJ3CyGIHnwXOFA","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• Organismos afectados (% susceptible\\Nantiguo vs. % con nuevo punto de corte):","guid":"BWLVltYSxcgMpcF90gmKEQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Proteus spp.: 100% vs. 65-85%.","guid":"FZdo8Aw4ARoJjvX81kOcHg","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Morganella morganii: 100% vs. 20-40%.","guid":"ok1cH2BMJm0gT3cIjWCBJQ","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Providencia spp.: 100% vs. 70%.","guid":"R1wIg4Rn_oAP5KNQjp0Vhg","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"• Serratia spp.: 99% vs. 93%.","guid":"Z642kv_qM-ffl2zq2J00hg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"1. Recomendado (++):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• B. fragilis","guid":"0Uszdzgb8w6zulqYU5utTQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• E. coli (ESBL)","guid":"uPzC89n3lMFGyyf5GBpImw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Klebsiella sp. (ESBL)","guid":"yTQfAEpqxPQNsiSutzu1iA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Nocardia sp.","guid":"s_U0KHLCbJa3fqLAAC3U0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"2. Activo (+):","guid":"Fkd2lt-A-OE_tTVGtFknIg","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Actinomyces sp.  • Aeromonas sp.  • Arcanobacter sp.  • C. freundii  • C. jejuni  • C. koseri  • Capnocytophaga sp.  • Clostridium\\Nsp.  • E. cloacae  • E. coli (S)  • E. faecalis (VS)  • Eikenella sp.  • F. necrophorum  • H. influenzae  • Kingella sp.  • Klebsiella\\Naerogenes  • Klebsiella oxytoca (S)  • Klebsiella pneumoniae (S)  • Leptospira sp.  • M. catarrhalis  • N. meningitidis  • P. acnes  •\\NP. aeruginosa  • P. multocida  • Peptostreptococci  • Prevotella sp.  • S. aureus MSSA  • S. epidermidis (MS)  • S. lugdunensis  •\\NS. saprophyticus  • Salmonella sp.  • Serratia marcescens  • Shigella sp.  • Staph coag-neg (MS)  • Strep. agalactiae gp (B)  •\\NStrep. anginosus gp  • Strep. gp C,F, G  • Strep. pneumoniae  • Strep. pyogenes gp (A)  • Viridans Strep.  • Y. enterocolitica","guid":"GIz6L_P1T0C-VFtu-lKzBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"1. PK/PD Index:","guid":"YBHji5u_X7d-_LiuazczkQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• T>MIC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"2. Preparaciones Farmacéuticas:","guid":"LWyWvyjGhDayeIbfDvLpTw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Inyección","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"49","text":"3. Absorción Oral (%):","guid":"XQvni8lWBRQCYnKsKdiLcw","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• N/A","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"49","text":"4. Tmax (hr):","guid":"NUk5HyN4KXgvuZnu5Ml3QQ","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"• N/A","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"49","text":"5. Concentración Máxima\\Nen Suero (µg/mL):","guid":"zfiqfPEAohBIUiW2K5TDeA","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• 40 µg/mL (500\\Nmg IV, SD)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"49","text":"6. Concentración Máxima en Orina (µg/mL):","guid":"n774Yu3Ep1rsZhHfIsTvug","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• N/D","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"49","text":"7. Unión a Proteínas (%):","guid":"1Vh40QAfMbVa-W7jaNYP5Q","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• 15-25%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"49","text":"8. Volumen de Distribución (Vd):","guid":"Iocny59S8xTZEkWvF7MDCw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• 0.23-0.31 L/kg","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"49","text":"9. Vida Media en Suero (T½ hr):","guid":"L5xWgD3-xdwcsRbYWGgrQQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• 1 hr","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"49","text":"10. Eliminación:","guid":"FWPU6N0mJPS5XJ8NkMMuHA","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Renal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"49","text":"11. Penetración en Bilis (%):","guid":"1LLTqMzQJ7-IC1RTPd2zfA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Mínima","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"49","text":"12. CSF/Sangre (%):","guid":"9gTuPczxx3CkgS1IYKoShQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• 8.5%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"49","text":"13. Niveles Terapéuticos en LCR:","guid":"4dBxoNM_NqXyxSRwBGu4qg","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Posiblemente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"49","text":"14. AUC (µg*hr/mL):","guid":"y6Fwzk5XHA-CkH6rcIXTgA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• 42.2 (500 mg IV, 0-inf)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones Medicamentosas\\NMediadas por Enzimas-Transportadores","guid":"dCezcUjx2mnHs1vedy1cpw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"1. Substrato de CYP450:","guid":"24OOj32YtolhQ9MTSImcrQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• No","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"2. Substrato de Transportador:","guid":"OMShRYG4W9I5g_3bjwC33g","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• OAT1, OAT3","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"3. Inhibición/Inducción de CYP450/Transportadores:","guid":"TgtQaBafpKWsGhGRue8tGA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"• N/A","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"4. Impacto en Concentraciones de\\NMedicamentos en Suero:","guid":"XcbllH9SRmP0n43rgm3s3w","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Carbapenems ↓ [ácido valproico] (inhiben acilpeptidasa\\N→ interrumpen reciclaje enterohepático)","guid":"ZyRxKGq6ugNqejMs9S1X1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones Medicamentosas\\NPrincipales","guid":"i0w-JLzhrze5r7TnNlsvWw","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"1. BCG:","guid":"S3KybA79XDE80xxEN-xhog","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• ↓efectividad → Evitar coadministración.","guid":"_joNAjiJ2501j90sbMMvQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"2. Ganciclovir:","guid":"H0RKdZwhrNyyO3SmPt5X4w","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• ↑riesgo de convulsiones → Monitorizar.","guid":"u8fhArnqhUHxnYPAWE_VoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"3. Probenecid:","guid":"91BpYqHcVB0tla8wRjmCUw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• ↑[Imipenem] → Monitorizar, ajustar dosis.","guid":"bXCFJ7NVh22AaISWyx04Sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"87","text":"4. Valganciclovir:","guid":"AmAwfKyXWOMUquhwA5fhlQ","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• ↑riesgo de convulsiones → Monitorizar.","guid":"L6sQ4gAvVqVHJcfPts7GKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"87","text":"5. Ácido Valproico:","guid":"aJUgZxx_rSN6Rh2TUtMLTA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• ↓[ácido valproico] → Monitorizar, ajustar dosis.","guid":"8v3kt_y2t_t-tj-CvzCHNw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":97,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Urología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Urología","filename":"Imipenem-Cilastatina-2024","id":"map_2381","resolved_references":[]}